<script>
$( function() {
var $curphase = '$$!CURRENT_PHASE$';

var $settings = $('#BranchListenerC1__ITM_C8616C4AE9D92B90202333');
var $settingsWrapper = $('#BranchTargetC1__ITM_C8616C4AE9D92B90202333');
var $help = $('#BranchListenerC1__ITM_C8616C4AE9D92B90233890');
var $helpWrapper = $('#BranchTargetC1__ITM_C8616C4AE9D92B90233890');
var $accounts = $('#BranchListenerC1__BranchAccounts');
var $accountsWrapper = $('#BranchTargetC1__BranchAccounts');
var $payments = $('#BranchListenerC1__BranchPayments');
var $paymentsWrapper = $('#BranchTargetC1__BranchPayments');

switch($curphase) {
    case 'Settings':
         $settings.addClass('bgActive');
         $settings.parent().addClass('bleft');
         $settingsWrapper.css('cssText', 'color: #229C7A !important;');
        break;
    case 'AccountsAndProducts':
        $accounts.addClass('bgActive');
        $accounts.parent().addClass('bleft');
        $accountsWrapper.css('cssText', 'color: #229C7A !important;');
        break;
    case 'Help':
       $help.addClass('bgActive');
       $help.parent().addClass('bleft');
       $helpWrapper.css('cssText', 'color: #229C7A !important;');
       break;
    case 'PaymentsAndTransfers':
        $payments.addClass('bgActive');
        $payments.parent().addClass('bleft');
        $paymentsWrapper.css('cssText', 'color: #229C7A !important;');
        break;
}

$settings.on('click', function(){
  $settings.addClass('bgActive');
  $settings.parent().addClass('bleft');
  $settingsWrapper.css('cssText', 'color: #229C7A !important;');

  $help.removeClass( 'bgActive' );
  $help.parent().removeClass( 'bleft' );
  $helpWrapper.removeAttr('style');

  $accounts.removeClass( 'bgActive' );
  $accounts.parent().removeClass( 'bleft' );
  $accountsWrapper.removeAttr('style');

  $payments.removeClass( 'bgActive' );
  $payments.parent().removeClass( 'bleft' );
  $paymentsWrapper.removeAttr('style');
})

$help.on('click', function(){
  $help.addClass('bgActive');
  $help.parent().addClass('bleft');
  $helpWrapper.css('cssText', 'color: #229C7A !important;');

  $settings.removeClass( 'bgActive' );
  $settings.parent().removeClass( 'bleft' );
  $settingsWrapper.removeAttr('style');

  $accounts.removeClass( 'bgActive' );
  $accounts.parent().removeClass( 'bleft' );
  $accountsWrapper.removeAttr('style');

  $payments.removeClass( 'bgActive' );
  $payments.parent().removeClass( 'bleft' );
  $paymentsWrapper.removeAttr('style');
})

$accounts.on('click', function(){
  $accounts.addClass('bgActive');
  $accounts.parent().addClass('bleft');
  $accountsWrapper.css('cssText', 'color: #229C7A !important;');

  $settings.removeClass( 'bgActive' );
  $settings.parent().removeClass( 'bleft' );
  $settingsWrapper.removeAttr('style');

  $help.removeClass( 'bgActive' );
  $help.parent().removeClass( 'bleft' );
  $helpWrapper.removeAttr('style');

  $payments.removeClass( 'bgActive' );
  $payments.parent().removeClass( 'bleft' );
  $paymentsWrapper.removeAttr('style');
})

$payments.on('click', function(){
  $payments.addClass('bgActive');
  $payments.parent().addClass('bleft');
  $paymentsWrapper.css('cssText', 'color: #229C7A !important;');

  $settings.removeClass( 'bgActive' );
  $settings.parent().removeClass( 'bleft' );
  $settingsWrapper.removeAttr('style');

  $help.removeClass( 'bgActive' );
  $help.parent().removeClass( 'bleft' );
  $helpWrapper.removeAttr('style');

  $accounts.removeClass( 'bgActive' );
  $accounts.parent().removeClass( 'bleft' );
  $accountsWrapper.removeAttr('style');
})


});
</script>
